{"tid":2033220,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"唔好再用「袋錢落你袋」嘅態度同台灣人溝通","createTime":"2020-05-24T13:47:42.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-26T10:53:39.000Z","uid":267201,"like":36,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"b3b97ba130e7c8d880cd3f7291ac6bb41f5ca954","tid":2033220,"uid":267201,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-24T13:47:42.000Z","msg":"前排台灣大選情勢緊急<br />\n大家係咁叫台灣人睇香港人示範之類係可以理解<br />\n<br />\n依家大選順利完結<br />\n一嚟證明咗台灣人並唔豬<br />\n二嚟對台灣人嚟講 香港人嘅利用價值係細咗<br />\n再叫呢啲態度叫台灣人知訂就會得罪人多<br />\n佢地憎中國 唔代表會一路同情香港<br />\n<br />\n另外<br />\n台灣的確有好多幫手足同香港嘅人<br />\n但從未為民主付出<br />\n就拎住前人嘅成果對香港冷嘲熱諷嘅仆街/五毛分化撚亦都存在<br />\n<br />\n我地無需要對台灣嘅支援有太多不必要嘅想像同要求<br />\n而事實上台灣已經好夠義氣幫咗我地好多<br />\n<br />\n要重新建立一個民族<br />\n我地最唔需要嘅就係敵人<br />\n所以我地要識得謙虛同將心比己<br />\n之前啲人打機同人嘈呀去旅行做閪客積返嚟嘅臭朵<br />\n無謂係呢場運動延續落去<br />\n<br />\n香港人建國"},{"pid":"0e0592a46f1972c49bb13229a8b94b934f946d00","tid":2033220,"uid":210794,"like":8,"dislike":1,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-24T13:51:44.000Z","msg":"Be humble"},{"pid":"d1d52182b5fc2aaa2e23fd7b2ff4e33ef67376c3","tid":2033220,"uid":14371,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-24T13:52:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b6df684b8b3daedaffa73acfc887958246fae109","tid":2033220,"uid":39470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-24T13:53:36.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1989acdac9017b1d71034a1d925baf369a85c39f","tid":2033220,"uid":286309,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-24T13:55:34.000Z","msg":"試下用番奶茶聯盟去connect"},{"pid":"8e57e50c61b9387389586b668fa68db3528af1f3","tid":2033220,"uid":3776,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"0e0592a46f1972c49bb13229a8b94b934f946d00","tid":2033220,"uid":210794,"like":8,"dislike":